text: Mhicca Carter (born 23 March 1990) is an Australian rules footballer who plays for West Coast in the AFL Women's (AFLW). She has also played women's rugby union domestically for RugbyWA in the Super W and internationally for the Wallaroos.https://wallaroos.rugby/players and coaches/mhicca carter ==References== ==External links== * * Category:Living people Category:1990 births Category:Rugby union fullbacks Category:Australian female rugby union players Category:Australia women's international rugby union players Category:West Coast Eagles (AFLW) players
